de.uka.ipd.sdq.beagle.judge

Class FinalJudgeBlackboardView

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uka.ipd.sdq.beagle.judge.FinalJudgeBlackboardView

  • public class FinalJudgeBlackboardView
extends java.lang.Object
    View of the Blackboard designed to be used by FinalJudge, therefore allowing reading access, remeasuring ResourceDemandingInternalActions, SEFFBranches, and SEFFLoops, and setting final expressions.
    See Also:
    for information about Blackboard views
